  "detailed_description": "<h1>✨Recommended by Light of Creators✨</h1><p><br><br></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1175720/extras/5e910814d03ef8ad7cabcf371553767c.poster.avif?t=1726113211\" width=600 height=204 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1175720/extras/5e910814d03ef8ad7cabcf371553767c.webm?t=1726113211\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1175720/extras/5e910814d03ef8ad7cabcf371553767c.mp4?t=1726113211\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Gerritory is a 4-player action party game with unique game rules and minimalistic visuals. You and your friends move cube characters in various levels and color tiles to score points.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >How To Play</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Move and color the tiles to score points.<br></li><li> Crush the superior players by stepping on them!</li></ul><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1175720/extras/774d9bfd826d078aa46675721fd1e134.poster.avif?t=1726113211\" width=300 height=204 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1175720/extras/774d9bfd826d078aa46675721fd1e134.webm?t=1726113211\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1175720/extras/774d9bfd826d078aa46675721fd1e134.mp4?t=1726113211\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1175720/extras/6549cc21f67ab999c6c0961b105edac3.poster.avif?t=1726113211\" width=300 height=204 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1175720/extras/6549cc21f67ab999c6c0961b105edac3.webm?t=1726113211\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1175720/extras/6549cc21f67ab999c6c0961b105edac3.mp4?t=1726113211\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Key Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Online & local play for up to 4 players.<br></li><li> Fill up the party vacancy with our most advanced AI players.<br></li><li> Unlock more than 40 levels with different tiles and features, and never get bored!<br></li><li> Additional level environments that challenge your skills.<br></li><li> Utilize various power-ups to win the game strategically.<br></li><li> Different match types: you can play either for a long session or just one single game.<br></li><li> Customize game objectives and environments in the custom match!<br></li><li> Play as different cute and stylish cube characters, be different from your friends!<br></li><li> Support keyboard remapping: 1 keyboard with 4 players is possible! (Still recommended to use controllers)</li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1175720/extras/5e910814d03ef8ad7cabcf371553767c.poster.avif?t=1726113211\" width=600 height=204 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1175720/extras/5e910814d03ef8ad7cabcf371553767c.webm?t=1726113211\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1175720/extras/5e910814d03ef8ad7cabcf371553767c.mp4?t=1726113211\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Gerritory is a 4-player action party game with unique game rules and minimalistic visuals. You and your friends move cube characters in various levels and color tiles to score points.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >How To Play</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Move and color the tiles to score points.<br></li><li> Crush the superior players by stepping on them!</li></ul><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1175720/extras/774d9bfd826d078aa46675721fd1e134.poster.avif?t=1726113211\" width=300 height=204 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1175720/extras/774d9bfd826d078aa46675721fd1e134.webm?t=1726113211\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1175720/extras/774d9bfd826d078aa46675721fd1e134.mp4?t=1726113211\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1175720/extras/6549cc21f67ab999c6c0961b105edac3.poster.avif?t=1726113211\" width=300 height=204 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1175720/extras/6549cc21f67ab999c6c0961b105edac3.webm?t=1726113211\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1175720/extras/6549cc21f67ab999c6c0961b105edac3.mp4?t=1726113211\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Key Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Online & local play for up to 4 players.<br></li><li> Fill up the party vacancy with our most advanced AI players.<br></li><li> Unlock more than 40 levels with different tiles and features, and never get bored!<br></li><li> Additional level environments that challenge your skills.<br></li><li> Utilize various power-ups to win the game strategically.<br></li><li> Different match types: you can play either for a long session or just one single game.<br></li><li> Customize game objectives and environments in the custom match!<br></li><li> Play as different cute and stylish cube characters, be different from your friends!<br></li><li> Support keyboard remapping: 1 keyboard with 4 players is possible! (Still recommended to use controllers)</li></ul>",
